    "title" : "When Treating Acute Pain, Prescribe No More Opioids Than Needed",
    "description" : "Please verify that the opioid order quantity and duration are no more than needed for the expected duration of pain severe enough to require opioids.\r\n\r\nFor guidance regarding prescribing opioids for acute pain, see [Recommendation 6 of the 2022 CDC Clinical Practice Guideline](https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/volumes/71/rr/rr7103a1.htm#Recommendation6).",
    "priority" : "urgent",
